AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#inSubset> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00000110> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/fbbt#cur>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00000110> "germ layer")
