AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00004047> "Min et al. (2021) - FBrf0248237 casually mention that the hypocerebral ganglion and the adjacent corpora cardiaca together contain approximately 35 neurons, including 20 Akh-expressing neurons, 5 mechanosensory neurons expressing Piezo, and 5 chemosensory neurons expressing Gr43a.")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00004047> "adult hypocerebral ganglion")
