AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0064777") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00004876> "Female germline cell which is the daughter of a female germline stem cell. It is found in region 1 of the germarium. It divides four times to give rise to 16 daughter cyst cells, which together form a germline cyst. Division is through a cleavage-like process, with the daughter cells being smaller than the parent cystoblast.")
