# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00004918> (calyx of oviduct)

AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0007735") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0207258") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0253444") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00004918> "The anterior-most, cup-shaped region of the lateral oviduct (Kapelnikov et al., 2008; McQueen et al., 2022). Formed by the joining together of the individual pedicels (small tubes coming from the base of each ovariole) (McQueen et al., 2022).")
