AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0064787") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0064803") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005042> "Precursor cell of the adult tracheal branches, found in the embryo or larva. Imaginal tracheoblasts originate from the spiracular branches in tracheal metamere 2 to 9, near the junctions with the transverse connectives and from several scattered positions in tracheal metameres 1 and 2.")
