# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005047> (tracheole)

AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0064787") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0087684") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0088947") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005047> "Terminal branch of the tracheal system. Tracheoles consist of fine cuticular tubes (around 1 micrometre in diameter or less) that extend from individual tracheolar cells. Tracheoles lack a mestracheon.")
