AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#inSubset> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005048> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/fbbt#cur>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005048> "Present at all developmental stages.")
