# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005317> (gastrula embryo)

AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0064803") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005317> "Embryo that is in the process of gastrulation (encompassing embryonic stages 6-8), during which complex morphogenetic movements result in the formation of the three germ layers; ectoderm, mesoderm and endoderm (Hartenstein, 1993).")
