AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#inSubset> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005511> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/fbbt#cur>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005511> "pars intercerebralis primordium")
