# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005799> (corpus cardiacum)

AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0053727") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0089570") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0178933") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0247015") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005799> "Neuroendocrine structure that forms part of the ring gland. In the embryo and larva it is found around the floor of the aorta, just anterior to the brain (Dai and Gilbert, 1991; de Velasco et al., 2004, Nassel and Zandawala, 2020). It migrates posteriorly during metamorphosis (Dai and Gilbert, 1991) and is found posterior to the brain, near the proventriculus, in the adult (Nassel and Zandawala, 2020). It produces Adipokinetic hormone from late embryo to adult stages (Lee and Park, 2004).")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005799> "UBERON:0001056")
AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0247015") <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005799> "CC")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasOBONamespace> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005799> "fly_anatomy.ontology")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#id> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005799> "FBbt:00005799")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#inSubset> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005799> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/fbbt#cur>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005799> "corpus cardiacum")
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005799> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005757>)
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005799> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000050> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00001718>))
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005799> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/RO_0002150> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00049645>))

# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005800> (corpus allatum)

AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0053727") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0064803") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0089570") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0179777") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0247015") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005800> "Neuroendocrine structure that forms part of the ring gland. In the embryo and larva it is found dorsal the aorta, anterior to the brain (Dai and Gilbert, 1991; de Velasco et al., 2004, Nassel and Zandawala, 2020). It migrates posteriorly during metamorphosis (Dai and Gilbert, 1991) and in the adult it is found posterior to the brain, dorsal to the corpus cardiacum (Nassel and Zandawala, 2020). It produces juvenile hormone (Dai and Gilbert, 1991; Hartenstein, 1993; Nassel and Zandawala, 2020).")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005800> "UBERON:0001057")
AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0247015") <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005800> "CA")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasOBONamespace> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005800> "fly_anatomy.ontology")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#id> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005800> "FBbt:00005800")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#inSubset> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005800> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/fbbt#cur>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005800> "corpus allatum")
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005800> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005757>)
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005800> ObjectSomeValuesFrom(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000050> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00001718>))

# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005801> (mushroom body)

AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0111409") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0224194") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0248215") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005801> "Bilaterally paired neuropil structure situated postero-dorsally in the protocerebrum that functions in olfactory associative learning and memory. The mushroom body is divided into: the calyx, which is closest to the cortex and receives sensory interneuron afferents; the pedunculus, which is a thick axon bundle extending from the calyx to the base of the lobes; and the mushroom body lobe system, which consists of a vertical branch and a medial branch, which have different structures at different life stages (Lee et al., 1999; Ito et al., 2014).")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005801> "UBERON:0001058")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005801> "VFB:FBbt_00005801")
AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0219809") <http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005801> "MB")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasExactSynonym> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005801> "corpora pedunculata")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasOBONamespace> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005801> "fly_anatomy.ontology")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#id> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005801> "FBbt:00005801")
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#inSubset> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005801> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/fbbt#BrainName>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#inSubset> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005801> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/fbbt#FB_gloss>)
AnnotationAssertion(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#inSubset> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005801> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/fbbt#cur>)
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005801> "This term as defined in Ito et al. (2014) corresponds to both the mushroom body (MB) and calyx (Cal) of Chiang et al. (2011).")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005801> "mushroom body")
SubClassOf(<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00005801> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/BFO_0000040>)
