AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FBC:DW") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0237252") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00007718> "Neuropil region where the larval tritocerebrum intersects with the centromedial longitudinal domain of the central nervous system (Hartenstein et al., 2018). It is found dorsal to the large ventromedial domain of the tritocerebrum and it flanks the esophageal foramen (Hartenstein et al., 2018).")
