AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00014814> "Manning and Krasnow (1993) assign the anterior spiracle to the mesothoracic segment, as we have done here, despite recording its origin as being from tracheoblasts associated with the humeral (dorsal prothoracic) disc.")
