AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00045047> "Despite the name, it is intended as a singular noun as in \"The United States\".")
AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:label <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00045047> "adult periesophageal neuropils")
