AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0180161") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0228122") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00047119> "Dorsal subdivision of the larval anterior commissure (Truman et al., 2004; Birkholz et al., 2015). It is thinner than the posterior dorsal commissure (Truman et al., 2004) and is found only in the three thoracic neuromeres (Birkholz et al., 2015).")
