# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00047120> (larval posterior intermediate commissure)

AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0180161") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0224770") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0228122") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00047120> "Intermediate subdivision of the larval posterior commissure (Truman et al., 2004; Birkholz et al., 2015). It is found in all thoracic neuromeres and, at a significantly reduced size, in the labial (S3) and A1 neuromeres (Birkholz et al., 2015). It is absent from the anterior gnathal ganglion (S1/S2) (Kuert et al., 2014).")
