AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0179777") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0193772") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0194938") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0204742") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0224194") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0244208") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0249161") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00049645> "Nerve that connects the corpus cardiacum to the brain (de Velasco et al., 2004; Dirksen et al., 2008; Mahishi and Huetteroth, 2019). These nerves contain the axons of neurosecretory cells of the central nervous system projecting to the ring gland and aorta (Hartenstein, 2006; de Velasco et al., 2007; Dirksen et al., 2008; Huckesfeld et al., 2021).")
