# Class: <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00052052> (female genital primordium)

AnnotationAssertion(Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0037847") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0040174") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0091028") Annotation(<http://www.geneontology.org/formats/oboInOwl#hasDbXref> "FlyBase:FBrf0141451") <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/IAO_0000115> <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00052052> "Ventral region of the genital disc that derives from abdominal segment 8 (Keisman et al., 2001). By third instar stage, it constitutes the majority of the disc in the female, but a much smaller proportion in the male (Keisman et al., 2001). In females, it produces the majority of adult female genital structures, in the male it produces a miniature eighth tergite (Keisman et al., 2001).")
