AnnotationAssertion(rdfs:comment <http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/FBbt_00100532> "Bayraktar et al. (2010) show that type I neuroblasts can be distinguished from type II neuroblasts as being Deadpan-, Prospero- and Asense-positive.")
